Support me on buymeacoffee if you like my work.

items.name: Koume Yukimi (Urara Meirochou)
items.description:
This character is a little more personal than my usual uploads. This is my feel-good character, from my feel-good anime. She is a crafty witch in training, with a creative flair, and has a major sweet tooth. If I ever had a kid, I hope they'd turn out like her. I've been using her as my discord icon for years and if you haven't seen her show, I'd highly recommend it for a casual laugh and feel-good vibes.

Back to the Usual:
This is a model that's based on the character Koume Yukimi from the anime Urara Meirochou. Tends to work best at 0.6. This model was trained on NAI anime-full-pruned and generated in Anylora. Made with the Kohya tool for AI Training through google colab. Any suggestions to improve or recommended things for the data set would be appreciated.

Some recommendations for her usual look:
yukimi koume, sleeveless shirt, medium breasts, off shoulder, short kimono, white kimono, twin tails, pink eyes, black hair, skirt, black shirt

to take off the kimono put these in negatives instead:
off shoulder, white kimono, short kimono

For her normal witch outfit:
yukimi koume, sleeveless dress, medium breasts, witch hat, twin tails, pink eyes, black hair, black dress

My other wildcards collections :

Nature And Techno Collection: A Fusion of Organic and Synthetic

Embrace the Intersection of Nature and Technology with the Nature And Techno Collection

The "Nature And Techno" collection is an intricately designed exploration of the harmonious and often complex relationship between the natural world and technological innovation. Through a blend of organic shapes and advanced machinery, this collection inspires creativity and opens doors to the future while staying rooted in the wonders of nature.

What's Inside? Over 700 items in a dozen wildcards!

Journey into a world that bridges the gap between nature and technology:

  • Natural Elegance: Organic shapes, weather effects, and textured beauty.

  • Mechanical Marvels: Robots, AI creatures, and technological advancements.

  • Environmental Exploration: Forests, oceans, and technologically enhanced landscapes.

  • Human Interaction: Emotions, actions, and connections with nature and technology.

  • Artistic Expression: From surreal to sublime, explore a variety of styles and concepts.

Usage:

Create your personal masterpiece:

  • Premade Prompts: Utilize NatureAndTechno/fullprompts for instant creation.

  • Custom Combinations: Mix and match elements from the bank to form your own narrative and visuals.

Examples:

  • Input prompt:

(best quality), portrait of a __bank/Creatures__, made of __bank/Organic_Shapes__, __bank/Colors__ __bank/Textures__ and __bank/Colors__ __bank/Technological_Elements__, in a __bank/Technological_Settings__, __bank/Natural_Settings__ in background, surreal, smooth and sharp details

  • Output prompt:

(best quality), portrait of a Artificial Intelligence Deer, made of Vines, Indigo Slick Surface and Blue Flash Drives, in a Observatory, Geyser in background, surreal, smooth and sharp details

  • Result image :

Instructions & Important Notes:

  • You need the SD Dynamic Prompt Extension. Put the files directly into the wildcard folder : sable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-dynamic-prompts\wildcards

  • Explore Multiple Themes: From eco-friendly cities to robotic animals, the possibilities are limitless.

  • Compatibility: All models are compatible. In fact, the result will depend greatly on the model used and the way it interprets the different elements of the prompt. So don't hesitate to run tests with different models.

Explore, Create & Share:

The "Nature And Techno" collection invites you to venture into a world where organic beauty meets technological marvels. Share your creations and connect with a community enthusiastic about this unique fusion. Don't hesitate to leave a review if you enjoyed the experience.

Future Plans:

Expect expansions, updates, and fresh themes as we delve further into this fascinating intersection.

Support & Feedback:

Reach out with thoughts, ideas, or contributions to the collection.

Conclusion

The "Nature And Techno" collection provides a platform for artists and thinkers to explore new terrains, bridging the organic with the synthetic. Whether you're an environmental enthusiast or a tech-savvy creator, this collection is your canvas. Dare to blend the natural with the technological.

Networks

You can find me on Instagram where I'm xploring the infinite canvas where art and technology intertwine, crafting AI-generated visuals that redefine the boundaries of imagination.

Thomasin McKenzie is a rising actress from New Zealand who had her breakthrough with "Leave No Trace" (2018), winning the National Board of Review Award for Breakthrough Performance. She also played a pivotal role in Taika Waititi's satirical comedy-drama "Jojo Rabbit" (2019). In 2021, she starred in "Old," "Last Night in Soho," and joined the televised adaptation of Kate Atkinson's novel "Life After Life." McKenzie's upcoming projects include portraying American gymnast Kerri Strug in "Perfect" and starring in "Eileen" alongside Anne Hathaway. Currently she plays the lead role in the television series "Totally Completely Fine."
